DESCRIPTION
===========

Here you find the project related news. When you want to include a new news
block write it above the other news, so the newest blocks are always at the
beginning.

The news have the following format:

DATE:        DD-MM-YYYY
TAG:         [PERSONAL] *
SUMMARY:     Short description about the news
DESCRIPTION: The full news text

* Please write here a suitable tag, for example [BUG], [PERSONAL], [RELEASE],
  [BUGFIX], ...


NEWS
====

DATE:        15-08-2008
TAG:         [BUG]
SUMMARY:     Major bug in search a name function
DESCRIPTION: During the search of a name the program terminates with a "Memory
             Corruption" or with "double free or corruption" exception. The
             error occurs only in the whitelist.
